  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies the default property for a component.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[

## Remarks
 Use the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultPropertyAttribute.Name> property to get the name of the default property.

 For more information, see [Attributes](/dotnet/standard/attributes/).



## Examples
 The following example defines a control named `MyControl`. The class is marked with a <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultPropertyAttribute> that specifies `MyProperty` as the default property.

